Package: smoothfs-samba-vfs
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         samba (= ${samba:Version})
Recommends: smoothfs-dkms
Description: Samba VFS module for smoothfs-backed SMB shares
 vfs_smoothfs is the Samba VFS module that lets smbd cooperate with
 smoothfs's tier-movement machinery: lease pin via `trusted.smoothfs.lease`,
 fanotify-driven oplock break on forced cutover, SMB FileId from
 `trusted.smoothfs.fileid`. Loaded into a share's VFS stack via
 `vfs objects = smoothfs` in smb.conf.
 .
 The module links against Samba's vendor-suffixed private ABI, so the
 binary is tied exactly to the Samba version it was built against —
 the Depends line pins the exact running Samba's `${samba:Version}`.
 Rebuild after any Samba upgrade; apt will refuse to install a
 mismatched pair.
